Business Brief -- Chips  Technologies Inc.:
   Settlement Reached in Suit
   Against Japanese Concern
A spokesman for Chips said litigation is pending against
OPTi Computer Inc., Elite Microelectronics Inc. and ETEQ
Microsystems, all based in San Jose. "The intent of the
litigation is not to raise a revenue stream from patents,"
the spokesman said. "The intent was to protect our patent
portfolio."